{"tid":2486787,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"立會直選新界將分5區、九龍3區、港島和離島合共2區   另設廢老關愛隊","createTime":"2021-04-13T06:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T13:49:22.000Z","uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf73104bad6ab0799ad3a0c1fa5a72c986fa78a","tid":2486787,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:20:52.000Z","msg":"政制及內地事務局長曾國衞去信立法會主席梁君彥，指明天將有關修改本港選舉制度的綜合條例草案，提交立法會大會首讀。政府下午會公布修訂選舉條例草案細節，消息指，立法會選舉直選選區將分成10區，每區有2席，新界會分為東南、東北、西南、西北和北區5區、九龍將分東、中和西3區、港島和離島合共2區，港島東包括灣仔和東區，港島南包括中西區、南區和離島。 <br />\n<br />\n消息指，草案將禁止鼓吹投白票或廢票行為，日後投票站將設有「關愛隊」安排，方便長者或有需要人士投票。另外，團體選民的團體要至少運作3年才有投票權。 消息亦指，候選人資格審查委員會，成員由行政長官委任，包括1位主席和2至4位委員，全部由主要官員出任。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2386984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2386984&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DKjg55e1U6BcW4s1L%2F%2F48L4%3D&h=1b59b5da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2386984</a>"},{"pid":"a47a32001d113f623a11a63e68df26c8360e7da5","tid":2486787,"uid":18477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:23:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">IRAN mode</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c061a31ac33df1ac60525291d412734277c53b5","tid":2486787,"uid":5502,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"其實唔使廢佬隊啦，唔會再好似19年咁多人投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9620e2a4c17d1f3b059a994cf74f0b5f43edce04","tid":2486787,"uid":268271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T06:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj